Simple python client to textalytics.com Social Media Analysis API

Extract relevant information from any kind of text.


Example Usage: 
------------- 
Use this command to analyze the contents of a text file and extract all relevant information 

   python myclient.py --file example.txt <key>

You need a <key> to call textalytics services. Register in the website to get your own
By default, all types of analysis are included. If you want to analyze only some fields provide values with --fields with fieldnames separated by | and enclosed between quotes 

For other uses:
-------------- 
   python myclient.py -h 


Description
-----------
myclient.py  - example client 
smaclient.py - help classes to wrap the API calls and the results 

